<section class="tier-section">
  <h2 class="tier-heading">Server pool tiers (reference)</h2>
  <div class="tier-table-wrap">
    <table class="tier-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Tier</th>
          <th>Pool bits (min)</th>
          <th>Buff idea</th>
          <th>Roll chance if eligible</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>0</td><td>0</td><td>None</td><td>—</td></tr>
        <tr><td>1</td><td>500</td><td>+1 extra drop / hour</td><td>40%</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2</td><td>1,500</td><td>Drop cooldown halved</td><td>55%</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3</td><td>3,000</td><td>Rare guaranteed in drops</td><td>60%</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4</td><td>6,000</td><td>Double burn value all day</td><td>65%</td></tr>
        <tr><td>5</td><td>12,000</td><td>All buffs combined</td><td>75%</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  <p class="tier-foot">
    Akira resets the pool after the daily roll, even when nothing procs — the community ride was still worth it.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .tier-section {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .tier-heading {
    font-family: "Zen Kaku Gothic New", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .tier-table-wrap {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--surface);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px var(--shadow-tint);
  }

  .tier-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
  }

  .tier-table th,
  .tier-table td {
    padding: 0.65rem 0.9rem;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .tier-table thead th {
    font-family: "Zen Kaku Gothic New", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--muted);
    background: var(--table-head-bg);
  }

  .tier-table tbody tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .tier-table tbody tr:hover td {
    background: var(--table-stripe);
  }

  .tier-foot {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .tier-table-wrap {
      overflow-x: auto;
    }

    .tier-table {
      min-width: 520px;
    }
  }
</style>
